...It was him. Was it? Was she merely seeing what her heart wanted to see? Had her hearts cravings taken over her mind and twisted reality into something other then what it truely was. Everything shut down. Details and actions slipped her mind, but she remained working on some basic level of existance. Some how she ended up at Derek's side. Didn't she? It wasn't certian. If he was hurt, she helped. If he wasn't, she was helping anyway.  <p><br>
