<br>
<br>
Mika had been amusing herself with a cockroach she found scurrying down the gutter.  she played a little game with it, flipping it over with her mind and watching it struggle to right itself.  then she would repeat the process, and ever so often, a faint giggle would escape her lips.  the game ended rather abruptly when, while she was trying to flip it over she pushed a little too hard and the poor insect exploded, sending green insect juice flying everywhere.  fortunatly she was far enough away that none of it hit her.  she sighed and tried to find something else to amuse her.  Usually when she was alone, she would meditate (years of which had given her the formidable mental powers that she now posessed) but she decided that what she really wanted right now was a cigarette.  now a days cigarettes came in all forms, the most common of which was a gelcap pill that you chewed on until it burst and filled you with the nicatene goodness.  this method eliminated second hand smoke which the gov't had outlawed years ago.  but Mika had a little nostalgia for the old days (even though she wasn't around that long ago) and preferred to smoke her cigarettes.  so, she flipped a smoke into her mouth and sparked it with her mind.  inhaling deeply, she closed her eyes and enjoyed the sensation, the repetative motions, the very act of smoking.<br>
<br>
When she had killed her smoke, she put it in the air in front of her and mentally threw it across the street and put it out against a small stone sign declaring the building behind it to be some kind of orphanage.  the building looked derelect and abandoned.  Mika knew that Neferetti was inside, she had known it for quite a while now.  Mika didn't know however wether or not she wanted to see her.  Over the last few months mika had become emotionally dead.  she wasn't sure what seeing Neffi again would do to her.  <br>
<br>
Mika got up and left.  she lived life (or tried to) without regrets.  so she tried to forget that she knew where neffi was.  she made her way back to the apt. she had found Carmen, Devin, and Jarron in.  As she climbed the stairs to the apt.  she yawned loudly, today had been a relatively eventful day and she was tired.  she was used to and comfortable with falling asleep anywhere, but tonight she hoped there was a bed for her.. . it had been so long since she had slept in a bed . . .<br>
<br>
she knocked on the door and waited for someone to answer . . .<br>
<br>
<br>
sinfuly yours,<br>
paradise perdu<br>
the true paradises are the paradises we have lost <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=13.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=13.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=13.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=13.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=13.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=13.topic&start=121&stop=121>7</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showPrevMessage?topicID=13.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showNextMessage?topicID=13.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=60><img src=http://Auction.2y.net/user/paradisetheheretic/addreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.emailToFriend?topicID=13.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.threadControl?topicID=13.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13.topic>